data.name: Cermet NERVA Fission

data.name: D-T Fusion Tokamak

data.rawText: Reactor 3 MASS 5 Rad-Hard D-T Fusion Tokamak

data.rawText: Reactor 2 MASS 4 Rad-Hard Lyman Alpha Trap

data.rawText: Reactor 0 MASS 4 Rad-Hard Free Radical Hydrogen Trap

data.name: Metallic Hydrogen
data.description: Hydrogen is predicted to form an atomic metallic phase in a metastable state at pressures >300 GPa.
data.rawText: Reactor 0 MASS 2 Rad-Hard Metallic Hydrogen

data.rawText: Reactor 1 MASS 6 Rad-Hard Pebble Bed Fission

data.description: The vaporized core of this reactor is contained in a transparent bulb. Power: 650 MWth Efficiency: 64%
data.rawText: Reactor 0 MASS 6 Rad-Hard VCR Light Bulb Fission
